		</p>
		<div class="flex flex-row items-start gap-4 sm:flex-row">
			<Button href="/about" title="More about me" action="primary" class="shrink-0" />
			<div class="flex items-center gap-x-4">
				<span class="hidden h-[2px] w-16 bg-black sm:block"></span>
				<SocialButton href="https://github.com/PickwickSoft/" class="hidden xs:block">
					<Icon name="github" />
				</SocialButton>
				<SocialButton href="https://de.linkedin.com/in/stefan-garlonta" class="hidden xxs:block">
